text: Anastasia Verkhoglyadova (born 12 June 1995) is a Russian water polo player. She played at the 2015 World Aquatics Championships, 2017 World Aquatics Championships, 2014 Women's European Water Polo Championship, 2016 Women's European Water Polo Championship. and 2018 Women's European Water Polo Championship. == References == Category:1995 births Category:Russian water polo players
